==================++====================================
 assets:cash      ||   $1000    $1000     $400    $1000 
 expenses:housing ||       0        0     $600        0 
 income           ||  $-1000   $-1000   $-1000   $-1000 
------------------++------------------------------------
                  ||       0        0        0        0 
>>>2
>>>=0

