hledger bal -M -b 2016-10 -e 2017-02 -f - --forecast=20160801-foobar
<<<
2016/12/31
    expenses:housing  $600
    assets:cash

~ monthly from 2016/1  salary
    income  $-1000
    assets:cash
>>>
>>>2
